        "font_size": 10.020000457763672,
        "header_level": null,
        "is_bold": false,
        "text": "The control baselines that have previously been included in NIST Special Publication 800-53 have been relocated to NIST Special Publication 800-53B. SP 800-53B contains security and privacy control baselines for federal information systems and organizations. It provides guidance for tailoring control baselines and for developing overlays to support the security and privacy requirements of stakeholders and their organizations. CNSS Instruction 1253 provides control baselines and guidance for security categorization and security control selection for national security systems."
      },
      "source_type": "Body",
